metadata.name: EA #1
metadata.description: 300 individual 1/1 art pieces featuring artists around Web3 space including and not limited to Ty Wright (Spiderverse), Kentasi, Cab (Spaceriders) and others. Each 1/1 piece also can be used as EA Pass (Eldora Pass). Eldora pass give you access to limited supply merchandise, top digital updates, alpha access and provides you with exclusive access to all new developments. Eldora Pass is a Founder Pass that puts you in charge.
